				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xilascrowe" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2969291); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2969291&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610252562" alt="XilasCrowe" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2969291)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xilascrowe" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2969291); return false;" >XilasCrowe</a></span> <span class="odate time_1553035466 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">19 Mar 2019 22:44</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4190501">
									

<p>For those of you who don't know, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2727655); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1553042297" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2727655); return false;">Weryllium</a></span> and I have a bet going. Every time he writes something longer than 1.5K words, I have to write something. Well, <a href="/scp-4789">SCP-4789</a> broke that, at like 1.7K or something. So, this is my response.</p>
<p>For some credits:<br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/panteradactyl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000286); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2000286&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1553042297" alt="Panteradactyl" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2000286)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/panteradactyl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000286); return false;">Panteradactyl</a></span> for loving this throughout its conception and always asking me when it was coming out<br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4022320); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1553042297" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4022320); return false;">RockTeethMothEyes</a></span> for being the first reader of the mostly finished product, and <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">hating</span> loving every second of this abomination &quot;I think I love it&quot;<br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jackalrelated" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3207203); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3207203&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1553042297" alt="JackalRelated" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3207203)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jackalrelated" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3207203); return false;">JackalRelated</a></span> for hating this with all his heart, and repeatedly bring it up in Discord &quot;nO. NO. ILLEGAL.&quot;<br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/proasek" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2048131); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2048131&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1553042297" alt="Proasek" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2048131)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/proasek" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2048131); return false;">Proasek</a></span> for basically writing my conprocs and stealing a co-authorship credit. Don't trust them.</p>
<p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/whitefinefire" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3179006); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3179006&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1553042297" alt="whitefinefire" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3179006)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/whitefinefire" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3179006); return false;">whitefinefire</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drleibowitz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5215978); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5215978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1553042297" alt="DrLeibowitz" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5215978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drleibowitz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5215978); return false;">DrLeibowitz</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alandaris" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3146689); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3146689&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1553042297" alt="AlanDaris" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3146689)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alandaris" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3146689); return false;">AlanDaris</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bluejones" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4646198); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4646198&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1553042297" alt="BlueJones" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4646198)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bluejones" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4646198); return false;">BlueJones</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaidypus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187161); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187161&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1553042297" alt="plaidypus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187161)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaidypus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187161); return false;">plaidypus</a></span>, and the other people who looked at this for looking at this <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">glorious creation</span> cursed abomination.</p>
<p>And yea, that's all I yote</p>

